{"tid":2397604,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係Carousell 俾人壓價就見得多，高價買野我都係第一次見","createTime":"2021-02-06T14:36:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T17:42:25.000Z","uid":291030,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7f64508bddc23f8a6486b9e49d9a386fbce8afba","tid":2397604,"uid":291030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T14:36:05.000Z","msg":"事源我放咗個舊Mon上去賣百幾蚊，但佢就開價$300，咁我都覺得有點奇怪，就問佢係唔係要<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Az5zbOD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAz5zbOD.png&h=9dd72f0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/95yXT2q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F95yXT2q.png&h=9ca98162&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住佢就係咁加錢加到$1000係旺角交收，我當唐嚇咗一嚇，一個都有反咁上下歷史既Mon，真係值得用1千買？<br />\n可能對佢有d咩特別既意義，咁我就問佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8YPj7sn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8YPj7sn.png&h=36d39bb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢又講唔出有咩特別原因，所以我冇理佢。<br />\n到咗第二日夜晚8點<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FCWRYDG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFCWRYDG.png&h=1c091eff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ej8En5q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fej8En5q.png&h=6ab934fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後佢仲加到$1200，我就冇理佢啦。"},{"pid":"f957dca572d2860d07f08cdfa91701f484e31bc6","tid":2397604,"uid":194298,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T14:37:41.000Z","msg":"南亞仔搶野，完"},{"pid":"918dcd6a304d34074f7542c24d630245b9a86823","tid":2397604,"uid":14337,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T14:41:29.000Z","msg":"係咪白卡佬玩野咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2613cc8f547e06fd4002d6762d11efe090488db7","tid":2397604,"uid":126382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T14:45:45.000Z","msg":"門檻低就多痴線佬，問題嚴重過以前yaho